{"data":[{"id":563823373,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"456ec3360bd65b63409c47a5dadcd60b","url_token":"lilin2bai","name":"lilin2白","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-bd23d35ba3f3b51168f419878f79d0f0_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-bd23d35ba3f3b51168f419878f79d0f0_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/456ec3360bd65b63409c47a5dadcd60b","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":1,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563823373","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546285368,"updated_time":1546285368,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e逻辑鬼才。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e高中生的推论分两段，第一段是证明变式1.2.3正确，第二段证明哥猜最小偶数为4。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e错的根源就是那个鬼才一般的逆否命题了，我就从逻辑角度分析。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我接着一个热评做个更详细的类比\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e原命题：若我妈是男的，则对于任意属于动物界（N+)的生命（n），能生育的生命（2n）属于雌性。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e逆否命题：存在一种属于动物界的生命，能生育但不属于雌性，则我妈是女的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后鬼才列举一个男性生育的例子，并且我妈是女的也是真，所以逆否为真，原命题为真。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这里有两点错误：1.男性生育并没有考虑进原命题，原命题和逆否命题存在不对等。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2.原命题需要有因果关系，否则求逆否命题以及由逆否命题判断真假是没有意义的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"逻辑鬼才。高中生的推论分两段，第一段是证明变式1.2.3正确，第二段证明哥猜最小偶数为4。错的根源就是那个鬼才一般的逆否命题了，我就从逻辑角度分析。我接着一个热评做个更详细的类比原命题：若我妈是男的，则对于任意属于动物界（N+)的生命（n），能生育…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_in